						<key>MacroActionType</key>
						<string>PromptForSnippet</string>
						<key>Text</key>
						<string>Hi %Ask:Name:20% and family,

Thank you for updating us. To move forward with your highlights, we need to shorten your plays. Typically, college coaches want to see your best plays within 4:30 minutes, and currently, your reel is at %Ask:Current Duration:15%. 

Please narrow it down to under 4:30 and we can continue editing from there. Let me know if you have any additional questions. </string>
						<key>TimeOutAbortsMacro</key>
						<true/>
						<key>Title</key>
						<string>Fill in the Snippet Fields</string>
					</dict>
